    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I considered adding direct support for delegates in the new formatting code, but it might be a bad idea.\r\n\r\nImplicit remoting relies on sending formatting data to the client and lets the client do the formatting. I don't think we want a formatting feature that would work in this scenario.\r\n\r\nThat said, formatting is already so slow that the overhead introduced here doesn't seem to be measurable.",
